{"tid":1388860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「重要」前線鐵馬嘅重要性","createTime":"2019-07-30T19:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T20:21:52.000Z","uid":100100,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4476ae437e2fa09de31ec9445d1dddfb535964a3","tid":1388860,"uid":100100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"我728係前線記得當時上環文華里同緊啲狗對峙，但係前面係完全冇鐵馬！一個都冇！<br />\n之後啲狗連放4,5粒蛋，前後都有，跟住就畜龍衝過黎咬人，仲有人落單被打。<br />\n我想講無論點都有鐵馬係前面。<br />\n冇錯，係有盾兵係前面幫手，但人地連放蛋之後再放畜龍用胡椒球槍，完全冇得打。<br />\n如果有鐵馬，就唔會比人一放畜龍就衝散，亦唔會有手足落單！<br />\n我明可能附近得返好少鐵馬，但希望係中後排嘅見到仲有鐵馬就幫手整定，以備不時之需。<br />\n仲有重要嘅係！唔該女仔上前面唔好再著背心，同埋係窄嘅街唔好再係咁逼入黎！上次文華里差啲人踩人！畜龍一衝個下完全係人夾人咁比人推住走！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最重要</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">退時麻煩一定要拉住前線嘅手足，唔好只顧自己，係咁一味向後退，救得一個得一個啊！唔該！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ee36f7030d60b3210079a0e2084a03a09fb9e0f","tid":1388860,"uid":100100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fe40cca1060e9067c1221dacf1d3a969bd48b344","tid":1388860,"uid":100100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3b0db02db84225e0e65297d6a1c5888f9d15590","tid":1388860,"uid":100100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95216c5774df04935bb4d1f334fb7cb39738225b","tid":1388860,"uid":100100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61f4c5c2bd235a70b1e48c95cb84babee0c23145","tid":1388860,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:02:32.000Z","msg":"一個卑微的請求：731 9點30東區法院 義士需要大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bec1711c85fbb6134a83412bcc22a02064660d08","tid":1388860,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:03:45.000Z","msg":"我地唔玩陣地戰 唔守<br />\nBe water<br />\n唔要用鐵馬守"},{"pid":"3c0b0558b0b31095e14d6f558bf80bbaca7ffb37","tid":1388860,"uid":100100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec1711c85fbb6134a83412bcc22a02064660d08","tid":1388860,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:03:45.000Z","msg":"我地唔玩陣地戰 唔守<br />\nBe water<br />\n唔要用鐵馬守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:06:32.000Z","msg":"唔係守 <br />\n而係上次係窄路到，前面冇嘢幫手阻一阻，令啲畜龍一衝就衝到。"},{"pid":"81eaff0ad2f9a872dd9035e4545ec0e24d0ede1c","tid":1388860,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a457c59409fc4bc1736f674d181f45ed0bcc816","tid":1388860,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec1711c85fbb6134a83412bcc22a02064660d08","tid":1388860,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:03:45.000Z","msg":"我地唔玩陣地戰 唔守<br />\nBe water<br />\n唔要用鐵馬守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:21:52.000Z","msg":"可以撞人 如果敢嘅話"}]}